This paper discusses the development and improvement of chatbots using Artificial Intelligence, which falls under the category of Natural Language Processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques to improve chatbots, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The proposed metric for computing dialog similarity also involves analyzing the structure of the dialog, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the use of chatbots for customer service, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
